WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:02.300
What a good show.

2
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.300
It’s all my fault.

3
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
I brought Xiaojie into the palace.

4
00:00:08.333 --> 00:00:11.200
I didn’t know he was so cruel.

5
00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:13.466
My own kin.

6
00:00:14.133 --> 00:00:15.033
I...

7
00:00:18.566 --> 00:00:19.666
I really regret it.

8
00:00:21.166 --> 00:00:21.966
Imperial Physician.

9
00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:25.166
How did I not notice his leniency in the past life?

10
00:00:25.166 --> 00:00:26.400
Such a pity.

11
00:00:26.466 --> 00:00:29.166
If Ruofeng had taken all the blame before his death,

12
00:00:29.333 --> 00:00:32.200
the consort would only be accused of mismanagement.

13
00:00:33.666 --> 00:00:36.766
Your Majesty, Consort Yan fainted

14
00:00:36.766 --> 00:00:39.100
because of overthinking and sorrow, leading to her illness.

15
00:00:39.366 --> 00:00:41.166
Since Consort Yan is so exhausted,

16
00:00:41.266 --> 00:00:43.300
she should stay in Zhongcui Palace and not come out.

17
00:00:43.333 --> 00:00:44.233
From today onward,

18
00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:47.366
remove Consort Mei.

19
00:00:48.166 --> 00:00:51.166
Consort, Consort, Consort!

20
00:00:51.466 --> 00:00:53.766
Fortunately, I prepared something in advance.

21
00:00:54.266 --> 00:00:56.366
But the Emperor is surprisingly generous.

22
00:00:59.100 --> 00:01:00.466
Since the truth has come out,

23
00:01:00.466 --> 00:01:02.033
I will take my leave first.

24
00:01:02.066 --> 00:01:04.600
The Inner Court still has matters for me to handle.

25
00:01:04.866 --> 00:01:06.300
I will take my leave now.

26
00:01:06.933 --> 00:01:09.500
I need to maintain my own safety.

27
00:01:10.366 --> 00:01:12.800
Otherwise, this emperor might think I’m easy to bully.

28
00:01:14.966 --> 00:01:17.266
It seems I really upset the Empress.

29
00:01:17.733 --> 00:01:19.966
Wait, I haven’t rewarded him yet.

30
00:01:19.966 --> 00:01:21.900
It’s fine, everyone, withdraw.

31
00:01:22.100 --> 00:01:24.266
Lord Shen, Your Majesty.

32
00:01:24.800 --> 00:01:27.166
I was so scared just now.

33
00:01:28.300 --> 00:01:31.000
I have some fine tea in my quarters.

34
00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:34.833
Why don’t you come back to the palace with me for a while?

35
00:01:39.966 --> 00:01:42.766
Mother, it seems I really angered Consort Rong.

36
00:01:42.766 --> 00:01:43.866
He has done well in Chang’an.

37
00:01:43.866 --> 00:01:45.833
I, hmph, serves him right.
